  "body": "Why do the docs on ReactLink say \"note that ReactLink is not needed for most applications and should be used cautiously.\"?\n\nhttps://facebook.github.io/react/docs/two-way-binding-helpers.html\n\nI assume having onChange handler on inputs is the preferred way to update state, and ReactLink, et al. just make that pattern a bit less boiler plate.   So I guess, I wanted to understand the note on the docs before I start using it.\n\nCheers, \n-john\n",
